From the first days we’d gather on campus to listen to online lectures and do HWs together. University was our safe heaven.
It wasn’t all fun and games. People here were extremely hardworking and did their best to understand the material. Despite many having a part-time job in addition to their studies everyone busted their ass and worked hard. The sight of student falling asleep from exhaustion was unimaginable but here this was usual.
